        <abstract> 
<p>Would welcome any facts on correlation, or GM’s criticisms. Explains how natural selection could produce apparent correlation of characters, but feels GM’s <hi rend="italic">Pelargonium</hi> example must arise from the leaves and petals being similarly affected at an early stage by an unknown cause.</p> 
        </abstract>
